text: Raimo Partanen (born 9 August 1940) is a Finnish skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1964 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Finland Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:People from Ruokolahti
